                     <interp inst="t17610225-13-person133" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , he came with a light, and we secured the prisoner.<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="176102250015"></xptr> These are the goods he had upon him, that are here produced.</p>
